    "updated_at": "2012-05-21T21:00:27Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think being able to change between them without a command line flag is useful, but I'm not sure that ever more menu items is the right UI for it. Should we think about some sort of configuration dialog for things like this?\n"
  },
