    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Of course - but there's an enormous wealth of features and options, and it would be completely overwhelming to have them all in the menu. Is this particular setting important enough to warrant a slot? It strikes me as the sort of rarely-changed option that could happily live in a settings dialog.\n"
